<!doctype html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Language" content="en" />
    <meta name="copyright" content="Creative Commons" />
    <meta name="distribution" content="global" />
    <meta name="googlebot" content="index,follow" />
    <meta name="robots" content="index,follow" />

    <meta name="publisher" content=".freefoundry" />
    <meta name="Designer" content="Joost Elfering" />
    <meta name="keywords" content="" />
    <meta name="description" content="" />

    <meta http-equiv="imagetoolbar" content="no" />

    <title><%= @nav %>.freefoundry</title>

    <link rel="shortcut icon" href="http://www.d-its.net/favicon.ico">
    <link href="/stylesheets/base.css" media="all" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />
    <!--[if IE]>
    <link href="stylesheets/iebh.css" media="all" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />
    <![endif]-->
    
    <script type="text/javascript" src="/javascripts/jquery-1.4.2.min.js"></script>
    <script type="text/javascript">
      jQ = jQuery.noConflict();
    </script>
    <%= javascript_include_tag :defaults %>
  </head>
  <body>
    <header class="exhebition">
      <div class="articleContainer">
        <div class="spacer">
          <div class="description">
            <article>
              <h1>What is .freefoundry?</h1>
              <div class="column">
                <p>The question should not be what, but who! Linking people together in an open and free environment to do what they like to do. Create musical instruments, collaborate on art pieces, helping out a local causes, plan performances and anything you can imagine. Innovating together in technology and growing personally in knowledge.</p>
                <p>We as .freefoundry ARE the platform on wich we do innovative, technological and fun projects. Together on Local and Global level. We find each other and collaborate on the future!</p>
              </div>
              <div class="column">
                <p>We want to enable the individual to contribute to the world on their own terms, level and field.</p>
                <p>Bla bla bla... we need more of this to make it interesting. Maybe some animations or a combined graph. Options we have, content we do not. This needs some love and attention.</p>
                <p>Sometimes it doesn't works</p>
                <p>Sometimes it does</p>
              </div>
            </article>
          </div>
          <div class="signUp">
            <h2>Come and join in.</h2>
            <p>Create a new account</p>
            <p>Use your:</p>
            <p>google account</p>
            <p>facebook account</p>
            <p>Already have an account? sign in!</p>
          </div>
          <div class="break"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="header">
        <div class="spacer">
          <nav>
            <ul class="navigation">
              <li<%= " class='opened'" if @nav == 'Home' %>><a href="/static/home">Home</a></li>
              <li<%= " class='opened'" if @nav == 'Projects' %>><a href="/static/projects">Projects</a></li>
              <li<%= " class='opened'" if @nav == 'Members' %>><a href="/static/members">Members</a></li>
              <li<%= " class='opened'" if @nav == 'News' %>><a href="/static/news">News</a></li>
              <li<%= " class='opened'" if @nav == 'About' %>><a href="/static/about">About</a></li>
            </ul>
          </nav>
          <img src="/images/logo-preview.png" alt=".freefoundry" class="logo" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </header>
    <div class="content exhebition gridlayout">
      <%= yield %>
    </div>
    <footer>
      <div class="toolbar">
        <div class="spacer">
          <div class="socialButtons">
            <ul>
              <li id="social_linkedin">
                <a href="http://www.linkedin.com/groups?gid=3202443" title="Connect with us on LinkedIn"><%= image_tag "transparent.gif" %></a>
              </li>
              <li id="social_facebook">
                <a href="http://www.facebook.com/pages/Freefoundry/150321324978822" title="Find us on facebook"><%= image_tag "transparent.gif" %></a>
              </li>
              <li id="social_twitter">
                <a href="http://twitter.com/freefoundry" title="Follow us on twitter"><%= image_tag "transparent.gif" %></a>
              </li>
              <li id="social_identica">
                <a href="http://identi.ca/group/freefoundry" title="Subscribe to us on identi.ca"><%= image_tag "transparent.gif" %></a>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>

